title: Roundabout for Fourteenth Street and Karadoc Avenue intersection (Mildura Rural City Council)
text: ( Source : Mildura Rural City Council ) Published on 15 October 2015 Work will start on construction of a roundabout at the intersection of Fourteenth Street and Karadoc Avenue next week. The busy Irymple intersection will be closed to traffic
